casebody.head_matter:
Eric Mel THOMPSON, et al., petitioners
v.
John AULT, Warden, et al.
No. 14-6559.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 17, 2014.
Opinion Motion of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperisdenied. Petitioner allowed until December 8, 2014, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of Rules of this Court.
